(5, '', 'Public offer', '<p>Agreement for the processing of personal data</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* - In accordance with the requirements of the Federal Law No. 152-ФЗ &ldquo;On Personal Data&rdquo; dated July 27, 2006, I agree to the processing of my personal data by the administration of the vera.fund resource without reservations and restrictions, performing actions with my personal data.&nbsp;<strong>3 Part 1, Article 3 of the Federal Law of July 27, 2006 No. 152-ФЗ &ldquo;On Personal Data&rdquo;</strong>, and confirm that, by giving such consent, I act freely, on my own will and in my interests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consent to the processing of personal data is given by me in order to obtain the services provided by the vera.fund resource</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The list of personal data for the processing of which consent is granted:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Surname</li>\r\n	<li>Name</li>\r\n	<li>middle name</li>\r\n	<li>Place of residence (city, region)</li>\r\n	<li>Phone numbers</li>\r\n	<li>Email addresses (E-mail)</li>\r\n	<li>as well as other personal data received from me.</li>\r\n	<li>I agree to carry out the following actions with all the indicated personal data:</li>\r\n	<li>collection</li>\r\n	<li>systematization</li>\r\n	<li>accumulation</li>\r\n	<li>storage</li>\r\n	<li>refinement (update or change)</li>\r\n	<li>using</li>\r\n	<li>depersonalization</li>\r\n	<li>blocking</li>\r\n	<li>destruction</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>as well as carrying out any other actions with personal data in accordance with applicable law.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data processing can be carried out both with the use of automation equipment, and without their use (with non-automatic processing). When processing personal data, the administration of the visacentermoscow.ru resource is not limited in the use of methods for their processing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I hereby acknowledge and confirm that, if necessary, the administration of the vera.fund resource is the copyright holder of all the photos and videos obtained during the event and is entitled to provide my personal data to third parties solely for the purpose of providing technical support services and (in an impersonal form) to statistical, marketing and other scientific purposes. Such third parties are entitled to the processing of personal data based on this consent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This consent is valid until the date of its withdrawal by sending a corresponding written statement signed by me, which may be sent by me to the administration of the vera.fund resource by mail by registered letter with acknowledgment of delivery, or delivered personally under receipt to the duly authorized representative of the vera.fund resource</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the case of receiving my written application to withdraw this consent to the processing of personal data, the administration of visacentermoscow.ru is obliged to stop processing them and to exclude personal data from the database, including electronic, with the exception of information about the last name, first name and patronymic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I understand that the use of the site vera.fund means my acceptance of the conditions described in it.</p>\r\n', 'en', 'oferta'),
(6, '', 'Privacy Policy', '<p>This Privacy Policy for personal data (hereinafter referred to as the Privacy Policy) applies to all information posted on the website at the address: http://vera.fund (hereinafter referred to as the Site), which visitors to the Site can receive about the User while using the Site , its services, programs and products.<br />\r\nThe use of the Site&rsquo;s services means the unconditional acceptance of the User with this Policy and the conditions for processing his personal information specified therein; in case of disagreement with these conditions, the User must refrain from using the services.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n1. <strong>GENERAL PROVISIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.1. In the framework of this Policy, the User&rsquo;s personal information means:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1.1.1. Personal information that the User provides about himself / herself when registering (creating an account) or in the process of using the Services, including the personal data of the User. Required to provide the Services information is marked in a special way. Other information is provided by the User at its discretion.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1.1.2. Data that is automatically transmitted to the Site&rsquo;s services during use by the software installed on the User&rsquo;s device, including the IP address, cookie data, information about the User&rsquo;s browser (or another program that allows access to the services), technical characteristics of the equipment and software used by the User, date and time of access to the services, addresses of the requested pages and other similar information.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1.1.3. Other information about the User, the processing of which is provided by the Agreement on the use of the Site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1.1.4. This Privacy Policy applies only to the Site http://vera.fund The Site http://vera.fund does not control and is not responsible for third-party sites to which the User can follow the links available on the Site http: // vera. fund<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n2. <strong>PURPOSES OF PROCESSING PERSONAL INFORMATION USERS</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.1. The site collects and stores only that personal information that is necessary for the provision of services or the execution of agreements and contracts with the User, except in cases where the law provides for the mandatory storage of personal information for a period specified by law.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2. The Site&rsquo;s personal information is processed by the Website for the following purposes:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.1. Identification of the User registered on the Site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.2. Providing the User with access to personalized resources of the Site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.3. Establishing feedback with the User, including sending notifications, inquiries regarding the use of the Site, provision of services, processing requests and requests from the User.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.4. Determine the location of the user to ensure security, prevent fraud.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.5. Confirmation of the accuracy and completeness of personal data provided by the User.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.6. Creating an account to use the capabilities of the Site, if the User has agreed to create an account.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.7. Notifications of the Site User about the capabilities of the Site, the activities of the site owner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.8. Providing the User with effective customer and technical support in case of problems related to the use of the Site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.2.9. Implementation of promotional activities with the consent of the User.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n3. <strong>CONDITIONS OF HANDLING PERSONAL INFORMATION USERS</strong>&nbsp;<strong>AND ITS TRANSFERS TO THIRD PARTIES</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.1. The site stores the personal information of users in accordance with the internal regulations of specific services.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.2. With respect to the personal information of the User, its confidentiality is maintained, except in cases where the User voluntarily provides information about himself for general access to the unlimited circle of persons. When using individual services, the User agrees that a certain part of his personal information becomes publicly available.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.3. The site has the right to transfer the personal information of the User to third parties in the following cases:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.3.1. User consented to such actions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.3.2. The transfer is necessary for the User to use a particular service or for the execution of a specific agreement or contract with the User.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.3.4. The transfer is provided for by Russian or other applicable law in the framework of the procedure established by law.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.3.5. In the event of the sale of the Site to the acquirer, all obligations to comply with the terms of this Policy with respect to the personal information received by him are transferred.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.4. The processing of the User&rsquo;s personal data is carried out without any time limit by any legal means, including in the personal data information systems using automation tools or without using such tools. The processing of users&#39; personal data is carried out in accordance with Federal Law No. 152-FZ of July 27, 2006 &ldquo;On Personal Data&rdquo;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.5. In case of loss or disclosure of personal data, the Site Administration informs the User about the loss or disclosure of personal data.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.6. The Site Administration takes the necessary organizational and technical measures to protect the User&rsquo;s personal information from unlawful or accidental access, destruction, modification, blocking, copying, distribution, as well as from other illegal actions of third parties.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.7. The Site Administration together with the User takes all necessary measures to prevent losses or other negative consequences caused by the loss or disclosure of the personal data of the User.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n4. <strong>OBLIGATIONS OF THE PARTIES</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.1. User must:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.1.1. Provide information about personal data required to use the Site.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.1.2. Update, supplement the information provided about personal data in the event of a change in this information.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.2. Site Administration is obliged to:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.2.1. Use the information obtained solely for the purposes specified in this Privacy Policy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.2.2. Ensure the confidentiality of confidential information, not to disclose without the prior written permission of the User, and not to sell, exchange, publish, or otherwise disclose the personal data of the User, except as provided for in this Privacy Policy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.2.3. Take precautions to protect the confidentiality of the personal data of the User in accordance with the procedure commonly used to protect this type of information in existing business transactions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4.2.4. Perform blocking of personal data relating to the relevant User from the moment of the request or request of the User or his legal representative or authorized body for the protection of the rights of subjects of personal data for the period of verification in case of unreliable personal data or illegal actions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. <strong>RESPONSIBILITY OF THE PARTIES</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.1. The Administration of the Site, which has not fulfilled its obligations, is liable for losses incurred by the User in connection with the unlawful use of personal data, in accordance with the legislation of the Russian Federation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.2. In case of loss or disclosure of confidential information, the Site Administration is not liable if this confidential information:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.2.1. Became public domain before its loss or disclosure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.2.2. It was received from a third party prior to its receipt by the Site Administration.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.2.3. It was disclosed with the consent of the User.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. <strong>SETTLEMENT OF DISPUTES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.1. Prior to filing a lawsuit in disputes arising from the relationship between the Website User and the Website Administration, it is mandatory to file a claim (a written proposal for a voluntary settlement of the dispute).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.2. The recipient of the claim shall, within 14 calendar days from the date of receipt of the claim, notify the claimant in writing of the results of the consideration of the claim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.3. If no agreement is reached, the dispute will be referred to the court in accordance with the current legislation of the Russian Federation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.4. The current legislation of the Russian Federation applies to this Privacy Policy and the relationship between the User and the Site Administration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. <strong>ADDITIONAL CONDITIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.1. The Site Administration has the right to make changes to this Privacy Policy without the consent of the User.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.2. A new Privacy Policy takes effect from the moment it is posted on the Website, unless otherwise provided by the new edition of the Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.3. The current Privacy Policy is located at: <a href=\"https://vera.fund\" target=\"_blank\">https://vera.fund</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.4. This Privacy Policy is an integral part of the Agreement on the use of the Site, located on the page at: <a href=\"https://vera.fund\" target=\"_blank\">https://vera.fund</a></p>\r\n', 'en', 'police_config');
INSERT INTO `1038_faqs` (`id`, `header`, `text`, `lands`, `icon`) VALUES
(1, 'Сколько стоит создание сайта?', '<p>Стоимость сайта зависит от многих факторов: объем, пожелания по дизайну, функционалу. Вы можете самостоятельно рассчитать стоимость вашего будущего сайта ответив всего на несколько вопросов.</p>\r\n', 'ru', '-'),
(2, 'Сколько времени делается сайт?', '<p>Лендинг делается от 5 дней. Многостраничные сайты делаются дольше, от 8 дней. На сроки и стоимость разработки влияют: 1. Сложность дизайна; 2. Количество страниц; 3. Количество блоков на странице; 4. Необходимость наполнения сайта товарами или услугами; 5. Сложность функционала; 6. Сложная анимация.</p>\r\n', 'ru', '-'),
(3, 'Как заказать у вас сайт? Расскажите про этапы, оплату?', '<p>1. Мы с Вами встречаемся и Вы подробно описываете задачу, важно привести примеры сайтов, которые вам нравятся по дизайну и заполнить бриф. Изучив информацию, я смогу сказать вам стоимость и сроки разработки сайта.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Заключаем договор в котором четко прописаны все детали проекта, сроки и стоимость.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Вы вносите предоплату 50% и я приступаю к работе над сайтом.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. В первую очередь я делаю прототип. Это подробный план расположения контента на сайте. Чтобы это сделать, я изучаю ваш бизнес, конкурентов, целевую аудиторию, выявляю УТП и создаю структуру и прототип вашего сайта.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Дизайн делается поэтапно. Вы можете следить за всеми изменениями на сайте онлайн и вносить комментарии и правки по ходу работы. Это помогает сэкономить время и избежать ситуации, когда дизайн вам не нравится и вы хотите его переделать. Я закладываю в стоимость время на небольшие правки, но если вы глобально меняете план сайта, его дизайн или добавляете несогласованные ранее новые блоки, это оплачивается отдельно.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. После утверждения работы вы оплачиваете оставшуюся сумму и я передаю вам все права доступа к сайту и материалы.</p>\r\n', 'ru', '-'),
(4, 'Как мне оплатить Вашу работу?', '<p>Я являюсь индивидуальным предпринимателем, по этому возможны любые способы оплаты: оплата наличными, перевод на карту, оплата на расчётный счёт.</p>\r\n', 'ru', ''),
(5, 'Вы работаете по договору?', '<p>Да, я работаю по договору и вместе с вами составляю техническое задание, которое ложится в его основу.</p>\r\n', 'ru', ''),
(6, 'How much does website creation cost?', '<p>The cost of a site depends on many factors: volume, wishes for design, functionality. You can independently calculate the cost of your future site by answering just a few questions.</p>\r\n', 'en', '-'),
(7, 'How long does the site take?', '<p>Landing is done from 5 days. Multi-page sites take longer, from 8 days.<br />\r\nThe timing and cost of development are affected by:<br />\r\n1. The complexity of the design;<br />\r\n2. The number of pages;<br />\r\n3. The number of blocks on the page;<br />\r\n4. The need to fill the site with goods or services;<br />\r\n5. The complexity of the functional;<br />\r\n6. Complex animation.</p>\r\n', 'en', '-'),
(8, 'Do you work under a contract?', '<p>Yes, I work under the contract and together with you I draw up the terms of reference that form its basis.</p>\r\n', 'en', '-'),
(9, 'How do I pay for your work?', '<p>I am an individual entrepreneur, so any payment methods are possible: cash payment, transfer to a card, payment to a current account.</p>\r\n', 'en', '-'),
(10, 'How to order your site? Tell us about the stages, payment?', '<p>1. We meet and you describe the task in detail, it is important to give examples of sites that you like in design and fill out a brief. Having studied the information, I can tell you the cost and timing of the development of the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. We conclude a contract which clearly spells out all the details of the project, terms and cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. You make a prepayment of 50% and I begin to work on the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. First of all, I am making a prototype. This is a detailed layout plan for content on the site. To do this, I study your business, competitors, target audience, identify UTP and create the structure and prototype of your site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Design is done in stages. You can follow all the changes on the site online and make comments and edits as you work. This helps to save time and avoid a situation where you don&rsquo;t like the design and want to remake it. I put in the time for small edits, but if you globally change the site plan, its design or add previously uncoordinated new blocks, this is paid separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. After approval of the work, you pay the remaining amount and I transfer to you all access rights to the site and materials.</p>\r\n', 'en', '-');
